co.cask.cdap.api.log

Class LogMarkerFilterList

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.api.log.LogMarkerFilterList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LogMarkerFilter

    public class LogMarkerFilterList
extends Object
implements LogMarkerFilter
    Implementation of LogMarkerFilter that represents an ordered List of LogMarkerFilter which will be evaluated with a specified boolean operator LogMarkerFilterList.Operator.MUST_PASS_ALL (!AND) or LogMarkerFilterList.Operator.MUST_PASS_ONE (!OR). Since you can use Filter Lists as children of Filter Lists, you can create a hierarchy of filters to be evaluated. Defaults to LogMarkerFilterList.Operator.MUST_PASS_ALL.
